OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will soon have a lot
OL,7,Fmore time on his hands - and I imagine
OL,8,Fhe'll want to spend some of it in the
OL,9,FLake District.
OL,11,FHe talked about family holidays there
OL,12,Fin successive Labour conference
OL,13,Fspeeches, and went for a walk there
OL,14,Fwith former football player Gary
OL,15,FNeville for a campaign video ahead of
OL,16,Fthe 2024 general election.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
