PN,32202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FHe even mentioned how he and his
OL,7,Ffamily had "made memories" in the
OL,8,FLakes in a recent press release
OL,9,Fannouncing discounts on children's
OL,10,Fmeals and entry to a range of
OL,11,Fattractions this summer.
OL,13,FIt's a little ironic, then, that I
OL,14,Fdon't think he's made an official
OL,15,Fvisit to our region as Prime Minister.
OL,17,FAnd time is now running out, after he
OL,18,Fannounced his resignation on Monday.
OL,20,FHis government will leave a lasting
OL,21,Flegacy in Cumbria, though.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
