OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FThey confirmed that the A66 will
OL,7,Fbecome dual carriageway all the way
OL,8,Ffrom Penrith to Scotch Corner.
OL,10,FMinisters say it will improve safety
OL,11,Fand reduce congestion, and work is due
OL,12,Fto begin before the end of 2026.
OL,14,FThey also pushed through plans for
OL,15,FCumbria to have a directly elected
OL,16,Fmayor with significant local powers,
OL,17,Fthough the first election has been
OL,18,Fpostponed until May 2027.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FBut they provoked rural uproar on both
OL,7,Fsides of the border with proposals to
OL,8,Fimpose inheritance tax on farm assets
OL,9,Fworth over #1m.
OL,11,FThat policy was eventually watered
OL,12,Fdown, and came into force in April
OL,13,Fwith a #2.5m threshold.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
