OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FCompared to his Conservative
OL,7,Fpredecessors, Starmer and his
OL,8,Fministers have had a much less
OL,9,Fconfrontational relationship with the
OL,10,FSNP Scottish Government, though the PM
OL,11,Fstruggled to cite any positive action
OL,12,Ffor the South of Scotland during my
OL,13,Finterview with him last autumn.
OL,15,FA chastening set of election results
OL,16,Ffor Labour last month, including at
OL,17,FHolyrood, helped seal Starmer's fate.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
