OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FAfter his own by-election triumph last
OL,7,Fweek, Andy Burnham looks set to
OL,8,Fsucceed him in Downing Street as soon
OL,9,Fas next month.
OL,11,FThe so-called 'King of the North', the
OL,12,Fformer Mayor of Greater Manchester has
OL,13,Flong talked about giving more powers
OL,14,Fto regional mayors, and perhaps the
OL,15,FScottish Parliament.
OL,17,FIn the last few days, his team has
OL,18,Frowed back on a previous suggestion to
OL,19,F"tear up" the Barnett Formula, which
OL,20,Fworks out funding for the devolved
OL,21,Fgovernments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,323,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FHe seems focused on rebalancing the
OL,7,FUK, by tilting investment away from
OL,8,FLondon and the South East - though you
OL,9,Fmay question how his interventionist
OL,10,Fcity region 'Manchesterism' would
OL,11,Ftranslate to our largely rural region.
OL,13,FHe has said that farm inheritance
OL,14,Fpolicy "does need looking at again".
OL,16,FAnd he's pledged to cut business rates
OL,17,Ffor pubs - but what about other parts
OL,18,Fof the hospitality and tourism sectors
OL,19,Fthat are so vital to Cumbria and the
OL,20,FSouth of Scotland?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
