PN,32208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1782733687
OL,3,CWhat does a new PM mean for Cumbria
OL,4,Cand the South of Scotland?
OL,6,FPreviously-expressed ambitions also
OL,7,Finclude bringing energy and water
OL,8,Fcompanies under public ownership.
OL,10,FWe should hear which policy positions
OL,11,Fhave survived to become pledges for
OL,12,Fgovernment when he gives speeches over
OL,13,Fthe next few weeks, before likely
OL,14,Ftaking over as Prime Minister on 20
OL,15,FJuly.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/8
